title: 243: Feeling Good Is Your Job with Gala Darling

description:
How do you manifest everything you want? Focus on feeling GOOD. Because when you feel good, you have more energy to go after the things that bring you joy. In this episode, I discuss manifestation, law of attraction and standing out like a bad-ass unicorn in the spiritual space with the one and only Gala Darling. This episode will inspire you to show ALL sides of yourself and be the unique queen that you are.
